steps.name: launch the url
User enter the username in user field
User enter the password in password field
User click the login button and it navigate to search page
User select the location in location field
User select the Hotels in hotel field
User select the required room type in room type field
User select the number of rooms in number of rooms field
User enter the Checkin date in checkin date field
User enter the checkout date in checkout date field
User select the number of adult room in adult per room field
User select the number of children per room in children per room field
User click the search button and it navigate to select hotel page
User click the radiobutton in select field
User click the continue button and it navigate to Book A Hotel Page
User enter the firstname in firstname field
User enter the lastname in lastname field
User enter the Address in Billing Address field.
User enter the credit card no in credit card no field
User select the card type in Credit Card Type filed
User select the month in Expiry Date Month field
User select the year in Expiry Date Year Field
User enter the CVV no in  CVV Field
User click the Booknow button and it navigate to booking confirmation page
